 dream</h3> <p class="multi-thumb-promo__summary gel-long-primer"> </p> </a> </li><li class="multi-thumb-promo__item" aria-role="listitem" data-item-count="68"> <a class="multi-thumb-promo__link" href="/sport/50562296">  <div class="multi-thumb-promo__media media-island"> <div class="gel-responsive-image gel-responsive-image--16by9"><!--[if !lte IE 8 | !IE]><!--><img class="sp-lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/{width}{hidpi}/cpsprodpb/0E60/production/_109908630_maidana_yb_m.png" data-sizes="auto" alt="Mercedes Maidana" /><!--<![endif]--><!--[if lte IE 8]><img src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/160/cpsprodpb/0E60/production/_109908630_maidana_yb_m.png" class="" /><![endif]--></div>  </div>  <h3 class="multi-thumb-promo__title gel-pica-bold">Self-destruction &amp; survival - the dark side of big wave surfing</h3> <p class="multi-thumb-promo__summary gel-long-primer"> </p> </a> </li><li class="multi-thumb-promo__item" aria-role="listitem" data-item-count="68"> <a class="multi-thumb-promo__link" href="/sport/football/50622330">  <div class="multi-thumb-promo__media media-island"> <div class="gel-responsive-image gel-responsive-image--16by9"><!--[if !lte IE 8 | !IE]><!--><img class="sp-lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/{width}{hidpi}/cpsprodpb/13672/production/_110147497_rapinoe_getty_promo_yb.png" data-sizes="auto" alt="Megan Rapinoe" /><!--<![endif]--><!--[if lte IE 8]><img src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/160/cpsprodpb/13672/production/_110147497_rapinoe_getty_promo_yb.png" class="" /><![endif]--></div>  </div>  <h3 class="multi-thumb-promo__title gel-pica-bold">The trailblazing winner who argued with Trump</h3> <p class="multi-thumb-promo__summary gel-long-primer"> </p> </a> </li><li class="multi-thumb-promo__item" aria-role="listitem"